{"tid":2184914,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[突發］Pelosi 被發現 違反禁令 冇帶口罩去Salon","createTime":"2020-09-02T02:24:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T02:50:49.000Z","uid":48083,"like":55,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"668f625a0dfee5dbe2f2ce5625f67c3088bb0f8e","tid":2184914,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T02:24:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hollandcourtney/status/1300898784344326144?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhollandcourtney%2Fstatus%2F1300898784344326144%3Fs%3D21&d=H6IDb39AroI58YjM1eqeYWHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=4b1d62db\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhollandcourtney%2Fstatus%2F1300898784344326144%3Fs%3D21&h=ad5034e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hollandcourtney/status/1300898784344326144?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/bbcworld/status/1300976569087913984?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbbcworld%2Fstatus%2F1300976569087913984%3Fs%3D21&d=H6IDb39AroI58YjM1eqeYWHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=131d3169\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbbcworld%2Fstatus%2F1300976569087913984%3Fs%3D21&h=78642346\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/bbcworld/status/1300976569087913984?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n原source<br />\n<br />\nEXCLUSIVE: House Speaker Nancy Pelosi visited a San Francisco hair salon on Monday afternoon for a wash and blow-out, despite local ordinances keeping salons closed amid the coronavirus pandemic, Fox News had learned.<br />\n<br />\nThe stylist doing her hair can be seen following her wearing a black face mask.<br />\n<br />\nSalons in San Francisco had been closed since March and were only notified they could reopen on Sept. 1 for outdoor hairstyling services only.<br />\n<br />\n'I am sharing this because of what everyone in my industry and my city ... is going through right now.'<br />\n<br />\n&mdash; Salon owner Erica Kious<br />\nSalon owner Erica Kious, in a phone interview with Fox News on Tuesday, shared details of Pelosi&rsquo;s visit. Kious explained she has independent stylists working for her who rent chairs in her salon.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wepNgpu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwepNgpu.jpg&h=4e9c3425&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.foxnews.com/politics/pelosi-san-francisco-hair-salon-owner-calls-it-slap-in-the-face\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fpelosi-san-francisco-hair-salon-owner-calls-it-slap-in-the-face&d=H6IDb39AroI58YjM1eqeYWHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=1421e576\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fpelosi-san-francisco-hair-salon-owner-calls-it-slap-in-the-face&h=8de07459\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.foxnews.com/politics/pelosi-san-francisco-hair-salon-owner-calls-it-slap-in-the-face</a>"},{"pid":"58eac73f09b6796f3525d08c9da4866452e2dd22","tid":2184914,"uid":30982,"like":162,"dislike":12,"score":150,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T02:29:09.000Z","msg":"等美國人自己搞算 佢有為幫過香港"},{"pid":"8064405ead7958a1be79f131d3dc9f7c17dc7a15","tid":2184914,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"58eac73f09b6796f3525d08c9da4866452e2dd22","tid":2184914,"uid":30982,"like":162,"dislike":12,"score":150,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T02:29:09.000Z","msg":"等美國人自己搞算 佢有為幫過香港"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T02:30:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22bc93b22e4d803e7fce740ddd5b32f85494b9fa","tid":2184914,"uid":141668,"like":94,"dislike":6,"score":88,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T02:35:37.000Z","msg":"一個唔好彩Biden當選，之後幾年可能就要靠佢"},{"pid":"625bb3ce94aa8442dd053752188f24e4ba